'''Amanita Design'''（蘑菇社）是一家捷克[[独立游戏|独立游戏]]開發商，總部位於[[捷克|捷克]][[布爾諾|布爾諾]]，2003年由{{link-en|雅库布·德沃斯基|Jakub Dvorský}}創辦<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://alternativemagazineonline.co.uk/2009/11/24/interview-in-conversation-with-jakub-dvorsky-founder-of-amanita-design-and-creator-of-machinarium/ |title=INTERVIEW – In Conversation With Jakub Dvorsky, Founder Of Amanita Design And Creator Of Machinarium {{!}} Alternative Magazine Online<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2020-10-15 |archive-date=2011-02-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110223233206/http://alternativemagazineonline.co.uk/2009/11/24/interview-in-conversation-with-jakub-dvorsky-founder-of-amanita-design-and-creator-of-machinarium/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。該公司曾開發《[[机械迷城|机械迷城]]》、{{link-en|銀河歷險記系列|Samorost}}和《[[植物精灵|植物精灵]]》等多款獲獎遊戲。

